query:
SELECT
                    id,
                    account_id,
                    quota_type,
                    event_type,
                    event_payload as "event_payload: Value",
                    event_time as "event_time: DateTime<Utc>"
                FROM account_quota_events
                WHERE account_id = $1
                  AND quota_type = $2
                  AND ($3::bigint IS NULL OR id > $3)
                  AND ($4::bigint IS NULL OR id <= $4)
                ORDER BY id
